These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red
City: marseilles, prague
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Color           | blood-red | blue |
| City   | marseilles       | prague  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, italian
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Color   | fuchsia       | ebony         |
| Nationality           | italian     | indonesian         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, ebony
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Cigar           | montecristo | tiparillo     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Color     | ebony         | coral   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, photographer
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, dancing
1. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Job   | software-developer   | photographer |
| Hobby           | baking | dancing    |

