The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, august
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, golf
1. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | tiparillo  |
| Birthday   | august   | july |
| Pet           | rat        | cat     |
| Sport         | climbing   | golf    |

