.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-16::.
2 different games are played: whist, chess
There 2 different types of food: lemon, strawberry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |
| Game    | chess     | whist           |
| Food        | lemon      | strawberry    |
| Birthday       | november    | december |
| Transport   | helicopter | bike          |

