The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, musician
There are 2 different nationalities: french, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the musician is on the left of the french##1
3. the doctor is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Pet      | rat    | goldfish      |
| Job   | musician   | doctor    |
| Nationality   | spanish | french     |
| Transport     | scooter | snowmobile |

