.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-19::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, december
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, van
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |
| Birthday      | december         | february         |
| Hobby   | camping      | rock-climbing      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | weightlifting |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | van           |

