.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, hiking
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
2 different games are played: go, bridge
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person playing go##1
3. the person playing go is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby      | hiking     | dancing |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Game   | bridge     | go     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 